    "title": "Samweli",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "samweli",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Samweli aliishi mwishoni mwa kipindi cha Waamuzi na alisaidia kuongoza Israeli wakati wa wafalme. Alikuwa mwamuzi wa mwisho wa Israeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:6\">1 Samweli 7:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:15-1Sam7:17\">15–17</a>). Samweli mara nyingi anachukuliwa kama nabii wa kwanza wa Israeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:20\">1 Samweli 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:24\">Matendo 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:20\">13:20</a>). Alihudumu kama kuhani (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:18\">1 Samweli 2:18</a>). Alikuwa mtu wa imani kubwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:32\">Waebrania 11:32</a>).</p><p>Samweli alizaliwa baada ya mama yake Hana kumwomba Mungu. Wazazi wa Samweli walisafiri kila mwaka kutoka Rama kwenda kwenye patakatifu huko Shilo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:3\">1 Samweli 1:3</a>). Katika patakatifu, Hana, ambaye hakuwa na watoto, alimuomba Mungu ampe mwana na akaahidi kumtoa kwa Mungu kwa huduma ya maisha yote (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:9-1Sam1:11\">1 Samweli 1:9–11</a>). Mungu alijibu maombi yake, na Samweli alizaliwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:19-1Sam1:20\">1 Samweli 1:19–20</a>). Samweli alipokuwa na umri wa kutosha, Hana alimpeleka kuhudumu katika patakatifu pamoja na Eli, kuhani mkuu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:24-1Sam1:28\">1 Samweli 1:24–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:11\">2:11</a>).</p><p>Wana wa Eli walikuwa waovu, lakini Samweli alimtumikia Bwana. Hivi karibuni ikawa wazi kwamba Mungu alizungumza kwa karibu zaidi na Samweli kuliko na Eli. Mungu alimwonya Samweli kuhusu maafa yanayokuja kwa familia ya Eli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:1-1Sam3:18\">1 Samweli 3:1–18</a>). Unabii huu ulitimia wakati Wafilisti walipowashinda Waisraeli, kuwaua wana wa Eli, na kuchukua Sanduku la Agano (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:1-1Sam4:22\">1 Samweli 4:1–22</a>). Baadaye, chini ya uongozi wa Samweli, watu walitubu kwa ajili ya ibada yao ya sanamu (kuabudu miungu ya uongo) na kushinda vita muhimu dhidi ya Wafilisti (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:3-1Sam7:17\">1 Samweli 7:3–17</a>).</p><p>Samweli alipoendelea kuzeeka, ilionekana wazi alikuwa na udhaifu sawa na Eli. Wana wa Samweli walikuwa waovu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:1-1Sam8:3\">1 Samweli 8:1–3</a>), na watu hawakutaka wao waongoze taifa. Badala yake, walimwomba Samweli kumteua mfalme kuwaongoza vitani dhidi ya maadui zao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:4-1Sam8:5\">1 Samweli 8:4–5</a>). Samweli kisha akamtia mafuta Sauli kama mfalme wa kwanza wa Israeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:1-1Sam10:24\">1 Samweli 9:1–10:24</a>).</p><p>Mabadiliko kutoka wakati wa Waamuzi hadi kuwa na wafalme yalikuwa changamoto. Samweli, kama kuhani, aliwaombea watu. Kama nabii, alimkosoa Sauli kwa kuwa na haraka na kutotii (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:5-1Sam13:14\">1 Samweli 13:5–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:12-1Sam15:35\">15:12–35</a>). Wakati Mungu alipomkataa Sauli kama mfalme, Samweli alimpaka mafuta Daudi kama mteule wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:1-1Sam16:13\">1 Samweli 16:1–13</a>) na kumlinda Daudi dhidi ya Sauli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:18-1Sam19:24\">19:18–24</a>).</p><p>Kupitia maombi na azimio, Samweli alikuwa kiongozi mwaminifu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:1\">Yeremia 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:32\">Waebrania 11:32</a>). Aliwahudumia watu wake kwa dhati na kwa ujasiri, na aliwakosoa wafalme na wazee. Aliunganisha Israeli kutoka katika mgawanyiko wa kikabila kuwa taifa lenye nguvu na kuanzisha mfumo wa utawala wa kifalme. Inawezekana aliandika <em>Rekodi ya Samweli Mwonaji</em> (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:29\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 29:29</a>). Aliandika kuhusu jinsi mfalme mzuri anavyopaswa kutawala (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:25\">1 Samweli 10:25</a>). Alipokufa, Waisraeli wote walimlilia. Alizikwa Rama, mji wake wa nyumbani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:1\">1 Samweli 25:1</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:19-1Sam2:11\">1 Samweli 1:19–2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:1-1Sam4:1\">3:1–4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:3-1Sam16:13\">7:3–16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:18-1Sam19:24\">19:18–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:1\">25:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:1-1Sam28:25\">28:1–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:6\">Zaburi 99:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:1\">Yeremia 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:24\">Matendo 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:20\">13:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:32\">Waebrania 11:32</a></p>",
